data.description: STUNNING pristine open floor plan. Features large gourmet kitchen with granite counter tops, 42'' cherry cabinets, stainlesssteel appliances & refrigerator stays. Beautiful slate flooring in the living area, kitchen, bath, utility room and hallway. 2'' fauxblinds. Granite counter tops in main bathrooms. A/C replaced in 2016. Extra large storage closet in master. Fully fenced back yard with covered patio,perfect for relaxing or entertaining. Close to shopping, schools and Grand Parkway.
